nodes.text: O'choa Detera was a female Zabrak dancer who performed in the cantina aboard Tansarii Point Station, where she and Mestral danced to the music of Alisia, Alitra, and Mako.
In 1 ABY, Mot Draken had a crush on her, but O'choa fell in love with Mot's friend Bun'Del.

O'choa Detera was a non-hostile NPC in the MMORPG Star Wars Galaxies prior to its closure on December 15, 2011. She could be found in the tutorial level on Tansarii Point Station added by the NGE update.
